            <th colspan="3">
              <strong>(A)</strong> Exempt amount subject to related trusts rules.<br>
              <strong>(B)</strong> Gains on carried interest taxed at 28% (32% in 2025–26).<br>
              <strong>(C)</strong> Increasing to 18% from 6 April 2026.
            </th>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>
